Je ferai la cueillette sans lui.

296
00:20:09,423 --> 00:20:10,617
La cueillette ?

297
00:20:11,983 --> 00:20:13,735
Oui, et celle de Petit Bob.

298
00:20:14,023 --> 00:20:15,138
